    <fluff>
        <overview>With Johnston’s facilities undamaged during the Capellans’ ejection from New Syrtis, the company expanded production as much as possible to prop up the faltering Davion military. Their new Axman was just a prototype in 3146, and only a lack of components stopped the Capellans from putting it into full production. Sharing a number of components with the Caesar -5D and Hatchetman -7D, the new Axman -5N is a terror at any range. The Tiburon Khanate-supplied HAG 20 and ER PPC allow it to deal damage as it closes, while triple ER medium lasers deal significant short-range damage. These weapons provide a number of ways to activate the ’Mech’s triple-strength myomers, allowing the -5N to close quicker and deal unholy amounts of damage in close combat.</overview>
