        <battlehistory></battlehistory>
        <deployment></deployment>
        <variants></variants>
        <notables>Si-ben-bing Sewarion Smirnow: A recent graduate from the Victoria Academy of Arms and Technology on Gunthar, Smirnow was thrust into the limelight during the Davion re-conquest of New Syrtis. After his Vindicator was damaged early in the battle, he acquired one of the Axman -5N prototypes to carry on the fight, and scythed his way through nearly two lances of the Illician Lancers’ Fifty-Ninth Striker Regiment as they tried to storm the Saso spaceport.:br::br::tab:Eventually forced to retreat, Smirnow and a few stragglers carried on guerrilla attacks against the Davions for another two months before retreating off-world in late February 3148. He would later put the ’Mech to good use against the Republic during the Operation Bàoyìng attacks the following year on Terra Firma, helping to finish off the second battalion of the Thirteenth Principes.</notables>
